description:
This is a 18 minute workout called '15 MIN FULL BODY PILATES HIIT || At-Home Workout With Weights (Warm Up & Cool Down Included)' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Move and sweat with me in this new Pilates HIIT Workout with weights!  Don't worry if you don't have weights, you can still do the workout without them. Or, if you want to get creative, you could fill up two bottles of water or any other household items to act as weights. Have fun! üòä
